| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0930 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8fd374fb-c43c-5d2c-a43e-82a6d6c2ced4"
